{"_id":"rQBEb5NAjEVSiRUi","name":"Consume Unlife","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>The mindless undead creature you touch is destroyed and you steal its death energy to heal yourself or the next ally you touch. The amount of damage healed is equal to the HP that the creature had remaining before you destroyed it.</p>","spellLevel":9,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"ZMyAQkXuqkMfIyEp","name":"Contagion","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Choose a creature you can see. Until you end this spell, the target suffers from a disease of your choice. While this spell is ongoing you take -1 to cast a spell.</p>","spellLevel":5,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"95lp64lzedRIg06S","name":"Control Weather","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Pray for rain—or sun, wind, or snow. Within a day or so, your god will answer. The weather will change according to your will and last a handful of days.</p>","spellLevel":7,"rollFormula":"","prepared":false},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"ptlaV9iGkSzpYMqT","name":"Cure Critical Wounds","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Heal an ally you touch of 3d8 damage.</p>","spellLevel":5,"rollFormula":"3d8","prepared":false},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"ptlaV9iGkSzpYMqT","name":"Cure Critical Wounds","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Heal an ally you touch of 3d8 damage.</p>","spellLevel":5,"rollFormula":"3d8","prepared":false},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"aEBd6p43tLHkpfz3","name":"Cure Light Wounds","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>At your touch wounds scab and bones cease to ache. Heal an ally you touch of 1d8 damage.</p>","spellLevel":1,"rollFormula":"1d8","prepared":false},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"AeXDPl3kBcN3mi5S","name":"Cure Moderate Wounds","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>You staunch bleeding and set bones through magic. Heal an ally you touch of 2d8 damage.</p>","spellLevel":3,"rollFormula":"2d8","prepared":false},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
{"_id":"92z5Q40Kr6cGmhu7","name":"Harm","permission":{"default":0,"Z8KGVPKcXF0jSV2e":3},"type":"spell","data":{"name":"","description":"<p>Touch an enemy and strike them with divine wrath—deal 2d8 damage to them and 1d6 damage to yourself. This damage ignores armor.</p>\n<p>Self damage roll: [[/roll 1d6]]</p>","spellLevel":7,"rollFormula":"2d8","prepared":false},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg"}
